original_title: Franco de Vita Vuelve Primera Fila
overview: Franco de Vita returns in: Primera fila is the fourth live album by Venezuelan singer Franco de Vita. The album was released on November 12, 2013 through digital download and on February 11, 2014 in physical form. Due to the success of his first album En Primera Fila, De Vita decided to release the second part of the same recording during the 10 and on July 11, 2013 at the Churubusco studios in Mexico City
title: Franco de Vita Vuelve Primera Fila
